The paper focuses on scene text detection using deep learning techniques, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The use of a fully convolutional neural network for learning the direction field suggests a focus on artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the limitations of classical segmentation-based approaches, indicating a potential focus on information retrieval (cs.IR) and natural language processing (cs.CL).
